triadRound1.text: Select in order of what you most agree with

options.text: I value ambition, efficiency and success.

options.text: I am conscientious and feel responsible for doing things the right way.

options.text: I seek the deeper emotional truth in every experience because raw, unfiltered feeling is what makes life meaningful

options.text: I am adaptable and know how to make a good impression.
I am adventurous and love exploring new ideas and experiences.

options.text: I am principled and have a strong sense of right and wrong.

options.text: I am generous and feel fulfilled by making others feel loved.

options.text: I find it difficult to relax when I see something that needs improvement or fixing.

options.text: I am different, or misunderstood, and often feel like I don’t fully belong.

options.text: I feel a strong sense of purpose when I’m being recognized for what I accomplish.

tieBreakers.text: Select which statement you most agree with

options.text: The world is imperfect, and it’s my responsibility to improve it.
The world is better when people feel valued and appreciated.
The world is full of opportunities for those who work hard and excel.
The world is full of beauty, but also a sense of longing and incompleteness.
The world is demanding, so resources must be protected.
The world is unpredictable, and security comes from being prepared.
The world is full of exciting possibilities to explore and enjoy.
The world is tough, and strength is needed to survive.
The world is easier when conflict and tension are avoided.

options.text: What’s more important is being responsible and ethical.
